%% System flow (3-lane swimlane) for MedRoute
flowchart TB
  subgraph PHC_Staff[PHC Staff]
    A1[Login]
    A2[Log Inventory]
    A3[View Dashboard & Alerts]
    A4[Request Redistribution]
  end

  subgraph District_Officer[District Officer]
    B1[View Pending Requests]
    B2[Approve / Reject]
    B3[Trigger Transfer Log]
  end

  subgraph State_Admin[State Admin]
    C1[View Analytics]
    C2[Manage Config]
  end

  A1 --> A2
  A2 --> A3
  A3 --> A4
  A4 -->|Creates request| B1
  B1 --> B2
  B2 -->|On Approve| B3
  B3 -->|Updates inventory & logs| A3
  B3 -->|Feeds data| C1
